ly in the world of baseball cards.;   Donruss' 1992cards are going to be available this week.;   Just think of it: Next season'sbaseball cards are beating some of this season's basketball cards to thestores.;   So what? Up against the Wall, it's always baseball season.; ' If wewin against Washington, I would think that we're as good as anybody; in thecountry.  ';   -- Michigan Coach Gary Moeller  </TEXT><BYLINE>  Information for this column was compiled from Mercury News wire services.Staff Writer Mike Antonucci contributed to this report.  </BYLINE><COUNTRY>  USA  </COUNTRY><EDITION>  Morning Final  </EDITION><CODE>  SJ  </CODE><NAME>  San Jose Mercury News  </NAME><PUBDATE>   911204  </PUBDATE> <DAY>  Wednesday  </DAY><MONTH>  December  </MONTH><PG.COL>  2C  </PG.COL><PUBYEAR>  1991  </PUBYEAR><REGION>  WEST  </REGION><FEATURE>  PHOTO  </FEATURE><STATE>  CA  </STATE><WORD.CT>  367  </WORD.CT><DATELINE>  Wednesday, December 4, 199100339107,SJ1  </DATELINE><COPYRGHT>  Copyright 1991, San Jose Mercury News  </COPYRGHT><LIMLEN>  1  </LIMLEN><LANGUAGE>  ENG  </LANGUAGE></DOC>